headline.main: Korean War Soldier Laid to Rest After Remains Found
headline.print_headline: Korean War Soldier Laid to Rest After Remains Found

lead_paragraph: A Korean War soldier whose remains were found 66 years after he went missing has been laid to rest with full military honors in Tennessee.
